# 📸 CodeAlpha Image Gallery

This project is developed as part of the Frontend Development Internship at CodeAlpha.

## 🚀 Project Overview

The Image Gallery is a responsive web application built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.  
It allows users to view images in a modern gallery layout with smooth transitions and navigation controls.

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript

## ✨ Features

- Responsive image gallery layout
- Hover zoom effects
- Smooth transitions
- Lightbox image preview
- Next and Previous navigation buttons
- Mobile-friendly design

## 📂 Project Structure

CodeAlpha_ImageGallery/
│── index.html
│── style.css
│── script.js
│── images/

## 🎯 Internship Task

Task 1: Image Gallery  
Frontend Development Internship at CodeAlpha

## 📱 Responsive Design

The project is fully responsive and works on:
- Desktop
- Tablet
- Mobile devices

